  "texts": [
    "Finally, a comprehensive structure for IDC course learning proficiencies was developed by combining the quantitative and qualitative results.",
    "The design of IDC course allowed students to select activities according to their interests, resulting in higher engagement and motivation through the learning creation process.",
    "The creation loop for learning habits, which is part of the IDC approach, helped students reinforce their learning efforts and sustain progress in listening and speaking.",
    "Furthermore, the flexibility and personalized learning approach of IDC potentially reduced anxiety and contributed to improved performance in the posttest.",
    "These combined factors demonstrate the positive impact of the IDC intervention on students' learning outcomes, leading to enhanced listening and speaking proficiency."
